equacy keeps us from changing the world. And believe me, we all have the power to change the world. If we only make the time. If we only free some head space.If you can''t learn to love yourself for yourself (and how could you with such a paradoxical motivation?)... then do it for us. Do it for the world. We need you. We need your mind. We need your attention. We need your thoughts. Change your focus, and you will (not can, but will) change the world. You already matter. You just have to realize it for yourself.', 5084, 0), (96227, 'A woman with vision is unstoppable, a woman who is always increasing her skills multiplies. Along with passion this woman is undeniable.', 8539, 0), (96228, 'Control what you can. Influence what you should. Forget the rest.', 4406, 0), (96229, 'A leader must stand up for his team even when he has to stand alone.', 7665, 0), (96230, 'Communication is the real work of leadership.', 19596, 0), (96231, 'Successful leaders leaders lead with passion and compassion.', 7665, 0), (96232, 'Go on your way , use you brain , be innovative, achieve your dreams and don’t turn back, because you left so many envious people behind you !! …', 19597, 0), (96233, 'Leaders are called upon to build not to repair.', 7665, 0), (96234, 'As we look ahead into the future, leaders will be those who serve others, actively listen, and daily empower.', 7665, 0), (96235, 'The ‘No Excuses’ mindset is not only composed of net worth, but also self worth and network.', 7665, 0), (96236, 'The gravitas in a leader is like clarity in diamond.', 5181, 0), (96237, 'Leadership is a choice. It is not a rank.', 19485, 0), (96238, 'We go from most doubted to most respected with the right outlook and attitude to life.', 19598, 0), (96239, 'At least half the job of CEO is communication - because of human nature. People fear what they don''t know. If the board wasn''t hearing that things were going well, they assumed that things must be going badly.', 11199, 0), (96240, 'While you''re 